sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as Operator or Runtime
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Queue as Queue Layer
    participant Loop as Packaged Worker Loop
    participant Worker as Worker Runtime
    participant Workflow as Workflow Runner
    participant State as State Root

    Operator->>API: POST /jobs
    API->>Queue: create_job(...)
    Queue->>State: Persist queued or scheduled job

    Loop->>Worker: run_next_job(...)
    Worker->>Queue: claim_next_job(...)
    Queue->>State: Mark job running and leased

    Worker->>Workflow: start_workflow or resume_workflow or start_child_workflow
    Workflow->>State: Persist workflow, child contract, and lineage state
    Workflow->>State: Refresh child synthesis, audit, and continuity-aware state

    alt Job succeeds
        Worker->>Queue: complete_job(...)
    else Job fails
        Worker->>Queue: fail_job(...)
    end

    Queue->>State: Persist final job state
    Worker->>State: Release worker lease
